We have been working very hard on this server for you players. You like to Pvp/Raid/Build/Create a team. PunishmenCraft is the place to be! We are a Faction server with a lot of friendly Staffs. Find your friends and get together to PvP other players or Raid together as a team and be the best faction out there! Lastly, Enjoy the server!
